Boats offer an alternative life style as there is limited water, electricity and sewage facilities. If you book to stay more than a few nights we will manage this for you. London Fields Park is 10 minutes away Parks are the best way to enjoy the city with children or for a short stroll. In London  Fields Park you will also find a Lido, open air swimming pool open all year. For the kids there is a large playground in Hackney Downs Park and a little and secluded one just at the back of the building. Electric vehicles chargers are 1 minute away

fields.host_about:
Hello!
My name is Tiziana and I have been living in London for 12 years.
I have lived in this lovely flat with my flat for several years and we just moved around the corner as we needed an extra bedroom.
It made us sad to leave our beautiful flat but we are sure you will enjoy it as much as we used to.
We are now a family of four and even if not originally from London we are really happy to live in this area.
We love to travel and found out about Airbnb ourselves once we were traveling to Spain and it was a great experience.

We are originally from Italy so most of our holidays are spent visiting family and friends over there. You will find plenty of Italian details in the flat, including a great moka and loads of Italian books.

We are happy to help you plan the perfect stay and excited to share our beautiful apartment with you
